{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/DGD_Header.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Dice Goblin's Den is a 2D side-scrolling Tower Defense game where you defend your fellow Goblins from waves of &quot;<i>heroes</i>&quot; who have been given quests at the local tavern to raid and loot your home! Gain new abilities as you unlock new classes by defeating enemy party leaders! Learn the quirks of each new class, and how their spells affect your units!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/GatherGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Resources_Dual_Choppers.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Gather resources, but be wary of the balance of allocating them between combat and worker units. It can be dangerous to spend too many resources trying to gain an advantage, but sometimes being greedy pays off!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/StrategizeGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/UnitOrder02.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Carefully place your combat units in strategic sequences that best complement your party leader's special abilities as well as the surrounding terrain!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/BuildGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Building01.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Build your way upwards with the resources your fellow goblins worked hard to gather, and overwhelm the enemy with your superior numbers! <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/DefendGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Defend02.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Destroy the enemy forces who are quested with the task of raiding your party and looting your corpses, but don't forget to keep your fellow goblins alive!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/UpgradeGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Upgrade01.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Upgrade your goblins by way of spells, abilities, and attributes at the cost of resources! But be careful not to put all of your dice in one basket! <i>Goblins together strong!</i><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/ClassesGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Classes01.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Unlock new classes to play when you defeat each enemy party leader! Each class has its own abilities that can alter your tactics and benefit your goblins in a unique way!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/LevelsGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Levels02.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Journey to the next level of your choosing! New levels means new enemies, differing resource allocations, and miscellaneous changes to adapt to!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/RogueliteGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Taunty_Goblin_Wizard_Spin_Promo.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Dice Goblins with all the uncertainty of Roguelite Mode! Play with randomized levels, party leaders, and enemy waves! Level up as you go and overcome various challenges along the way, but be careful! Defeat will set you right back to the drawing board!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Coming_SoonGif.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Coming_Soon.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Coming soon to a Goblin's Den near you!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/Wishlist_It_Color_2.gif?t=1731467868\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731467868","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/page.bg.jpg?t=1731467868","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/5642a0d0019c3d3715ef9c24a7a9ade6794166fd/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731467868","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/5642a0d0019c3d3715ef9c24a7a9ade6794166fd/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731467868","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196940/extras/DGD_Header.gif?t=1731467868\" /><br>Dice Goblin's Den is a 2D side-scrolling Tower Defense game where you defend your fellow Goblins from waves of &quot;<i>heroes</i>&quot; who have b